OL,3,CGovernment to announce digital ID card
OL,4,Cscheme to curb 'illegal migration'
OL,6,FDigital ID cards are expected to be
OL,7,Fannounced by Keir Starmer as early as
OL,8,FFriday, in the government's latest
OL,9,Fattempts to curb illegal immigration.
OL,11,FThe scheme would be subject to
OL,12,Fconsultation and thought to require
OL,13,Flegislation, the iPaper first reported.
OL,15,FIn practice, it would allow the
OL,16,Fverification of a citizen's right to
OL,17,Flive and work in the UK and anyone
OL,18,Fstarting a new job or looking to rent
OL,19,Fa home would be required to show their
OL,20,Fdigital ID.
