OL,6,FIt would then be checked against a
OL,7,Fcentral database of people entitled to
OL,8,Flive and work in the UK.
OL,10,FThe new scheme, it is hoped, would
OL,11,Freduce the attraction of working in
OL,12,Fthe UK illegally, including for
OL,13,Fdelivery companies.
OL,15,FIt comes amid calls from French
OL,16,FPresident Emmanuel Macron for the UK
OL,17,Fto reduce "pull factors" for migrants
OL,18,Fto make the crossing to the UK.
