OL,6,FStarmer is due to speak at the Global
OL,7,FProgress Action Summit in London
OL,8,Falongside Australian Prime Minister
OL,9,FAnthony Albanese and Canadian Prime
OL,10,FMinister Mark Carney on Friday.
OL,12,FThe UK has only previously had
OL,13,Fmandatory ID cards during wartime and
OL,14,Fthe last tranche was scrapped in 1952.
OL,16,FSir John Major's government ran a
OL,17,Fconsultation on reintroducing them in
OL,18,F1995, but they were never brought in.
