OL,6,FIn the report, it said: "The Labour
OL,7,Fgovernment has the opportunity to
OL,8,Fbuild a new piece of civic
OL,9,Finfrastructure, something that would
OL,10,Fbecome a familiar feature of daily
OL,11,Flife for everyone in the country.
OL,13,F"It would support better enforcement
OL,14,Fof migration rules, and protect
OL,15,Fvulnerable British citizens from being
OL,16,Fwrongly denied their rights."
