OL,6,FBut the move has again been met with
OL,7,Fbacklash across the board.
OL,9,FThe civil liberty group Big Brother
OL,10,FWatch has again warned against their
OL,11,Fintroduction.
OL,13,FA petition started by the group has
OL,14,Freached more than 101,000 signatures.
OL,16,FIn a letter to Starmer on Wednesday,
OL,17,Fthe group said: "Mandatory digital ID
OL,18,Fis highly unlikely to achieve the
OL,19,FGovernment's objective of tackling
OL,20,Funauthorised immigration.
