OL,6,F"The proposed schemes fundamentally
OL,7,Fmisunderstand the 'pull factors' that
OL,8,Fdrive migration to the UK and would do
OL,9,Fvery little to tackle criminal people-
OL,10,Fsmuggling gangs or employers and
OL,11,Flandlords who operate 'off the books'.
OL,13,F"Instead, it would push unauthorised
OL,14,Fmigrants further into the shadows,
OL,15,Finto more precarious work and unsafe
OL,16,Fhousing."
